steps.name: Given Guest User should be on michaels home page
When User should enter the "Small Kraft Box by Celebrate It™" product in search bar
When Click on search button to see the list of products
Then User should Click on the product "Small Kraft Box by Celebrate It™" from list
When User should select shipping method SDD from PDP page
Then "sdd" radio button selected and radio button text is "Same Day Delivery"
When User should click on add to cart button
When User Should be click on view cart button
When User should click on checkout button
When User will get model popup to click on continue as guest user
When User should provides Delivery information like  Name, Last Name, Address,City,State,Zip code,Email ID and Phone number
When User will add the Card Details like Name on Card,Card Number,Expiration Date,CVV
When User will click on Place order button
When User will redirected to Order Confirmation Page
